Robin Rose Bennett, &quot;Healing Magic: A Green Witch Guidebook to Conscious Living, 10th Anniversary Edition&quot;

ISBN: 1583948376 | 2014 | EPUB | 264 pages | 5 MB


Filled with stories, songs, rituals, recipes, meditations, and trance journeys that outline more than 100 ways to practice the art of magical healing, this guidebook to conscious living by renowned herbalist Robin Rose Bennett makes it easy to follow the path to physical and spiritual health. In the tradition of natural witchcraft, Healing Magic, 10th Anniversary Edition presents step-by-step instructions for conducting earth-centered rituals, preparing herbal remedies, and casting spells to enchant and heal as well as advice on cooking everyday meals incorporating health-enhancing herbs and home remedies
